治光譜闊D, 認受性會多D"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T17:17:18.000Z","msg":"無錯！其實就係想做到呢個效果。<br />\n文武都要升級<br />\n<br />\n好想啟發大家思考<br />\n<br />\n政治光譜方面，都好希望唔同人會參與，兼聽則明。"},{"pid":"23a51c3e46f0b51184f5a22f0e6eb80af313ed14","tid":1642342,"uid":17016,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T17:22:08.000Z","msg":"一推再推 認同請分享"},{"pid":"4bc7df66c4f45c8c7a2fb99a8eff8bb7ad3378a9","tid":1642342,"uid":17016,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T17:25:21.000Z","msg":"和理非研討會想要人呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8c8c6b0c6d3b7e1e4f2deed1e82bbaa8fa76053e","tid":1642342,"uid":59676,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T17:27:53.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8092701c19a015c1067b61b26b2fdc6750735e8c","tid":1642342,"uid":17016,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T17:31:12.000Z","msg":"要人呀！！！"},{"pid":"85defdb54c85244581a351bfaa5f8f041598420b","tid":1642342,"uid":17016,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T17:37:02.000Z","msg":"推到有人"},{"pid":"64633ba5f8e02e9a9ec894d697a2ebccc4b21724","tid":1642342,"uid":17016,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T17:57:46.000Z","msg":"係咪tldr<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9a7ea0e0888346baf8238fa0773f58ae7ec810ba","tid":1642342,"uid":17016,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T18:08:30.000Z","msg":"再推 政事台正經po無人睇？"},{"pid":"9ddeb239ffa0367c4d5bb27e0945e8600875508e","tid":1642342,"uid":72253,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T18:28:05.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"7ad215a97ad39641bed1cf4f58477db8e5ecea2e","tid":1642342,"uid":73082,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T20:47:48.000Z","msg":"終於出現了"},{"pid":"f0534b